Package: smokinguns
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, smokinguns-data (= ${source:Version}), libgl1-mesa-glx
Description: Quake 3 engine based "Old West's" game
 Smokin' Guns is intended to be a semi-realistic
 simulation of the "Old West's" great atmosphere & was
 developed on Id Software's Quake III Arena Engine.

Package: smokinguns-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, smokinguns (>= ${source:Version})
Description: Quake 3 engine based "Old West's" game (server package)
 Smokin' Guns is intended to be a semi-realistic
 simulation of the "Old West's" great atmosphere & was
 developed on Id Software's Quake III Arena Engine.
 .
 This package contains the server binary.

Package: smokinguns-data
Architecture: all
