Description: Quake 3 engine based "Old West's" game (data package)
 Smokin' Guns is intended to be a semi-realistic
 simulation of the "Old West's" great atmosphere & was
 developed on Id Software's Quake III Arena Engine.
 .
 This package contains the data files.
